`,(0,v.jsx)(t.p,{children:"Given my fairly poor skills in graphical design, it seems like a bit of a strange choice for me to build my own bespoke website. However, that is all a matter of perspective. A lack of skill is an opportunity for growth. I've spent most of my professional career in a full stack role for either web or mobile apps. In that time I've almost always had a design, a framework chosen for me, and a team of more talented front end specific developers to lean on. This meant that much of my time was in integration and in the data layer. I've never built a rich website from scratch on my own, styling and all."}),`
